${1:*} TODO ${2:🞎}$0
:PROPERTIES:
:ID: `(org-id-new)`
:TYPE: d0305c80-3399-4e07-b4ba-ee8c22eacb19 Iteration
:EFFORT: 0:00
:END:

*$1 Context

- MAY define a list of materials or references to
  materials that clarify the following content.

*$1 Objective

- MUST define WHAT we want.

*$1 Test

- SHOULD define new assertions to be verified,
  provided the objective is claimed to be reached.

*$1 Plan

- MAY define steps — i.e. a tree of assertions — at
  the end of which the objective is reached.

*$1 Risks

- MAY define a list of risks — i.e. assertions that
  MUST NOT be verified.

*$1 Log

- MAY define a list of notable propositions discovered
  during this iteration execution.

*$1 Checklist

- [ ] Stakeholders updated.
- [ ] Time has been logged.

*$1 Result

- MUST provide a quick summary of the result and links
  to artifacts, if any.

*$1 Review

- Demo is reproducible by the client
- Feedback

*$1 Sign-off

- Client acceptance: [YES/NO]
- If milestone → invoice issued
- Next iteration planned

*$1 Retrospective

- Liked: what went well
- Learned: new insights / techniques
- Lacked: what was missing / painful
- Longed for: what we wish we had
- Action Items: what should be carried forward
